{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 16,
  "title": "第十六章（歸根）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "致虛極，"
    },
    {
      "text": "守靜篤，"
    },
    {
      "text": "萬物並作，"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾以觀其復。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫物芸芸，"
    },
    {
      "text": "各復歸其根，"
    },
    {
      "text": "歸根曰靜，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂覆命。"
    },
    {
      "text": "覆命曰常。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知常曰明；"
    },
    {
      "text": "不知常，妄作凶。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知常容，"
    },
    {
      "text": "容乃公，"
    },
    {
      "text": "公乃王，"
    },
    {
      "text": "王乃天，"
    },
    {
      "text": "天乃道，"
    },
    {
      "text": "道乃久。"
    },
    {
      "text": "沒身不殆。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "得道之人，捐情去欲，五內清靜，至於虛極。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "守清靜，行篤厚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "作，生也。萬物並生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言吾以觀見萬物無不皆歸其本也。人當念重其本也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "芸芸者，華葉盛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言萬物無不枯落，各復反其根而更生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "靜謂根也。根安靜柔弱，謙卑處下，故不復死也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言安靜者是為復還性命，使不死也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "覆命使不死，乃道之所常行也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能知道之所常行，則為明。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不知道之所常行，妄作巧詐，則失神明，故凶也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能知道之所常行，去情忘欲，無所不包容也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無所不包容，則公正無私，眾邪莫當。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "公正無私，可以為天下王。治身正則形一，神明千萬，共湊其躬也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能王，德合神明，乃與天通。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德與天通，則與道合同也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "與道合同，乃能長久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能公能王，通天合道，四者純備，道德弘遠，無殃無咎，乃與天地俱沒，不危殆也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
